The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Metro | Good Morning
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       Good Morning
      Hello It's Sunday , July 20 , 2008                
	Conference    Attend a conference on Educational and Economical Development at Moulali Youth Centre, 5pm.    
	Workshop    Take your kids to a workshop on sand art at Starmark, South City Mall, 11am to 1pm.         
	On Stage    Enjoy Chokh Gyalo at Madhusudan Mancha, 6.30pm.         
	exhibition    Check out drinking water purification systems at an exhibition at The Peerless Inn, 10am.        
	Fashion    Drop in at Monsoon Magic, an exhibition of saris, jewellery, accessories and home linens, at Soumyas Creation, 10.30am to 7pm.         
	Fair Draw    Check out the Home, Kitchen and Lifestyle Fair at Ice Skating Rink, 11am to 8pm.        
	Eye on Art    Browse through Art Mela at Gallery Exposure, 3pm to 8pm.  Stop over at a show of paintings at Academy of Fine Arts, 3pm to 8pm.   Move on to a painting show at Birla Academy of Art and Culture, 4pm to 8pm.                                                                                                                                                              
